{"tid":1074414,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【勁擦雜種鞋】蘋果 CEO 到訪北京：感謝中國打開大門！","createTime":"2019-03-23T11:18:42.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-23T13:53:49.000Z","uid":1886,"like":1,"dislike":17,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"ac2c7d4087ab467714edb92afb31b02cc8bc9861","tid":1074414,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-23T11:18:42.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/realtime/article/20190323/59402052\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190323%2F59402052&d=INFrb%2BpCZNVkt1J9J2ljEPGl%2B26pDsgLotMYn9d4AWI%3D&h=5da12249\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190323%2F59402052&h=c4263b11\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/realtime/article/20190323/59402052</a><br />\n<br />\n蘋果（Apple）行政總裁庫克（Tim Cook）今日在北京出席2019中國發展高層論壇，他說：「我們看到中國不斷發展變化，感謝中國打開大門，讓我們成為這個市場上的一份子。」<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20190323/large/1553316790_b4d1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20190323%2Flarge%2F1553316790_b4d1.jpg&h=99d665c4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">GAY COOK到訪北京，感謝中國打開大門。</span></div>"},{"pid":"c46a81470b4cd3a83d5f2c0351acb23218747472","tid":1074414,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-23T11:19:06.000Z","msg":"「我非常贊同習近平主席所說的，眾人拾柴火焰高。」庫克說，當前世界正在面對前所未有的挑戰，譬如氣候變化，貧困問題，以及不平等加劇，數百萬人沒有獲得基本醫療挑戰。同時，庫克強調，世界也有巨大的機遇，有潛力可以在保證地球的健康時，實現繁榮的經濟，同時給可以給每個人提供學習的機會。<br />\n<br />\n要實現這些目標，庫克指出，就需要政府、教育機構和企業同心協力。庫克表示，蘋果相信技術可以讓世界變得更美好，也認為有責任為應對這些挑戰貢獻一己之力。蘋果公司為200萬個開發者和創業者提供工具，幫助他們開發應用程序。<br />\n<br />\n蘋果公司還提供很多教育機會。庫克稱，相信這是推動社會公平發展的最大機遇，「我們在中國就看到了改變。」另外，庫克稱，蘋果公司100%利用可再生能源，也在幫助供應商朝着這個方向努力。他說：「我們強調夥伴關係的力量。相信開放和互信是關鍵，這樣才能產生思想和解決方案。我們看到中國不斷發展變化，感謝中國打開大門，讓我們成為這個市場上的一份子。」"},{"pid":"6386c8144be6bef975954d57674d8d75eaeb4809","tid":1074414,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-23T11:19:17.000Z","msg":"庫克又指，鼓勵中國繼續開放，開放對發展來說至關重要。「開放不僅對中國發揮潛力來說很重，也對全球整體經濟繁榮至關重要。」最後，他引用馬丁路德金（Martin Luther King Jr.）的名言：「共同的命運讓我們牢牢綑綁在一起。」庫克指，不管有甚麼直接發生在一個個體上，都會間接影響到整體的人類，「我們的未來密不可分，我們的未來取決於合作。」"},{"pid":"e8ea56b4d20787d337c4112cce16589ed7a9b0c9","tid":1074414,"uid":3457,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-23T11:19:30.000Z","msg":"即去中國開間叫橙 再告尻蘋果侵權"},{"pid":"d47e3e5f170e4a05ca244483bc6f050d3d250ca7","tid":1074414,"uid":42340,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-23T11:22:15.000Z","msg":"粉果:用家問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"46b99b9091cc87c24f57e57fb8bd22670dde0c17","tid":1074414,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-23T11:27:08.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: blue;\"></span>"},{"pid":"12f2d9e82f7d7747040e949831bacfc54ec9087f","tid":1074414,"uid":10692,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-23T11:32:19.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"dc7a9cd4a3056f7ee3a7809740d2e7bf47d4268a","tid":1074414,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-23T11:49:38.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: blue;\"></span>"},{"pid":"e89ca0b1a5540c6e28bd076ce42b3db5ee2e405d","tid":1074414,"uid":224066,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-23T11:49:57.000Z","msg":"IPHONE係中蟈賣得唔好呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1c83420933fc546e757345986414754b499864c8","tid":1074414,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-23T13:46:32.000Z","msg":"<strong></strong>"},{"pid":"7df08974fc316cde7f2da98ad34e340fbf541fb8","tid":1074414,"uid":36134,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-23T13:47:51.000Z","msg":"Idog表示睇唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"48af31181387433bed51582f8c8b8408321360da","tid":1074414,"uid":191926,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-23T13:53:49.000Z","msg":"佢同豬西 2個<br />\n日日係度不務正業 江河日下<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n成日吹捧支那，習主席前，習主席後<br />\n(好撚多矽谷精英都係對住特朗普就扮撚哂人權鬥士<br />\n對住仲衰的支那就<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />) &nbsp;"}]}